WEBVTT

00:51.375 --> 00:52.459
Don't worry.

00:52.959 --> 00:54.626
Leopard won't come this way.

00:56.626 --> 00:57.709
Are you sure?

00:59.459 --> 01:03.000
It won't hurt you unless
it felt threatened.

01:26.876 --> 01:28.709
The movie got over late.

01:28.876 --> 01:30.626
I figured you might have slept.

01:30.667 --> 01:33.792
Roy had told him to get back
as soon as it gets over.

01:34.042 --> 01:35.167
Where is Roy uncle?

01:35.209 --> 01:37.250
He has gone for some meeting.

01:38.209 --> 01:39.792
Have breakfast with us, Sony!

01:39.918 --> 01:41.459
We have already eaten.

01:41.751 --> 01:43.876
Dad will be waiting to go
to the farm.

01:45.209 --> 01:47.125
Sony, Have you got
any poetry books?

01:47.751 --> 01:50.584
He has entered a poetry
recitation at school

01:50.959 --> 01:52.083
When is it?

01:52.125 --> 01:54.709
21st, next Tuesday.

01:55.918 --> 01:57.042
We don't need a book.

01:57.083 --> 01:58.751
I'll come this Saturday
and teach him.

02:04.500 --> 02:05.584
Subin

02:06.542 --> 02:07.959
Sony is leaving.

02:10.751 --> 02:11.918
Subi

02:12.918 --> 02:14.250
See you on Saturday.

02:20.459 --> 02:21.417
Alright.

03:24.959 --> 03:26.542
Heard that you've resumed old habits.

03:26.626 --> 03:27.751
What habits?

03:27.959 --> 03:29.083
Smoking and Drinking.

03:29.292 --> 03:30.542
Who told you all this?

03:30.999 --> 03:34.042
You don't have to convince me.

03:34.918 --> 03:36.083
Then why do you ask?

03:36.125 --> 03:37.417
My questions are the problem now?

03:39.500 --> 03:40.918
Do you talk to Sony nowadays?

03:41.918 --> 03:43.334
Any idea what's in his mind?

03:43.375 --> 03:45.542
When I ask him anything
he turns mute.

03:45.999 --> 03:47.626
That's because he
is afraid of you.

03:47.792 --> 03:49.918
He talks properly to others.

03:50.542 --> 03:52.375
We let him study for a
year as he wanted.

03:54.459 --> 03:57.667
And when I ask him to look for
another job, he doesn't like it.

03:57.918 --> 04:00.125
He used to run
a tuition center,right?

04:00.959 --> 04:02.292
It was of no use.

04:02.334 --> 04:04.834
If it's a salaried job,
he could be at ease.

04:05.542 --> 04:08.000
I'll have a word with
the Vicar General

04:08.500 --> 04:10.334
Give me a couple of months.

04:11.125 --> 04:13.999
I'll figure out something by Easter.

04:15.250 --> 04:16.999
If there is an expense,
we'll take care of it.

04:18.125 --> 04:19.751
They will take it from his salary.

04:19.792 --> 04:21.751
You stop drinking if you can.

04:23.125 --> 04:25.125
Stop making an alcoholic out of me.

04:30.417 --> 04:31.667
Dear Everyone,

04:31.876 --> 04:34.626
Our dear son Ditto,

04:34.959 --> 04:38.375
Is being welcomed by his
rightful brother-in-laws,

04:48.042 --> 04:50.792
Next is the beautification ritual,

04:51.542 --> 04:53.999
For which we invite the barber on stage.

04:56.751 --> 05:01.792
All men above the age of seventeen,

05:02.751 --> 05:04.709
Shall I beautify the groom?

05:05.125 --> 05:06.667
Can't hear you!

05:07.375 --> 05:11.999
All men above the age of seventeen,

05:12.250 --> 05:14.792
