05:15.292 --> 05:16.834
Can't hear you!

05:17.999 --> 05:22.250
I'm asking the men above
seventeen years

05:22.918 --> 05:26.250
Shall I beautify the groom, Ditto?

05:26.626 --> 05:28.125
Yes, you may!

07:23.999 --> 07:29.959
"The season has come"

07:30.042 --> 07:34.500
"On your children who roam"

07:34.667 --> 07:38.959
"Protect them keenly"

07:38.999 --> 07:43.209
"With your showers of mercy, St. Thomas"

07:43.250 --> 07:46.959
"Silk and homespun fabrics"

07:46.999 --> 07:49.667
"Pearl necklaces"

07:49.709 --> 07:52.667
"On decorated marquee"

07:52.709 --> 08:00.125
"Come help us, St Thomas"

08:00.209 --> 08:04.500
"On decorated marquee,
come bless us"

08:11.834 --> 08:15.375
"Wood, Stones, Gold, and Silver"

08:15.459 --> 08:18.959
"Copper and Iron, ever filling the mind"

08:18.999 --> 08:24.042
"Works to be done ever and more"

08:28.209 --> 08:32.250
"In pride, the dear
ones would do it"

08:42.042 --> 08:44.959
"In unity, the dears ones
in front of you"

08:44.999 --> 08:47.083
"This way it goes"

10:48.959 --> 10:49.834
What's happening?

10:49.876 --> 10:51.334
It's the old lady's cow.

10:51.876 --> 10:52.709
Where?

10:52.792 --> 10:53.834
In the pit.

11:01.459 --> 11:02.459
Here

11:03.042 --> 11:03.999
Hold

11:04.417 --> 11:05.626
Lift up

11:05.876 --> 11:09.834
Though it's for the leopard,
an elephant can fit in here.

11:12.125 --> 11:13.792
I think that its spine is fractured.

11:14.083 --> 11:15.751
We'll pull it up somehow.

11:19.250 --> 11:21.042
There's a rope at Pilla's house

11:22.125 --> 11:23.792
We'll send someone.

11:24.250 --> 11:26.876
Unni must have some
stuff with him.

11:26.918 --> 11:27.999
I'll try calling him.

12:15.709 --> 12:18.999
Pull it up!

12:21.542 --> 12:23.125
Bring it here!

12:26.209 --> 12:31.042
[Indistinct chatters]

12:31.083 --> 12:33.999
Wait

12:39.167 --> 12:41.042
Okay, let it loose.

12:41.417 --> 12:43.125
Slowly release it now.

13:02.334 --> 13:04.292
[Indistinct chatters]

13:11.375 --> 13:14.667
[Indistinct chatters]

13:29.792 --> 13:32.417
Did you close down your
tuition centre?

13:32.459 --> 13:33.709
Yeah, I did.

13:34.459 --> 13:36.876
Stephy finds maths a bit difficult.

13:37.542 --> 13:40.125
She can manage other subjects.

13:40.500 --> 13:41.792
But math is not easy.

13:42.709 --> 13:44.250
That can be taken care of.

13:45.125 --> 13:49.542
If you can take two classes per week,
it will be good right?

13:50.626 --> 13:52.375
Yeah, they'll be fine.

13:53.626 --> 13:55.125
How much do you charge?

13:55.834 --> 13:58.667
I don't set fees for my acquaintances.

13:58.959 --> 14:00.959
You may set an amount yourself.

14:00.999 --> 14:02.751
Shall we start next week?

14:02.792 --> 14:03.375
Yeah,

14:04.792 --> 14:05.959
I'll come by.

15:54.292 --> 15:55.667
Leave it there, Aunty!

15:56.459 --> 15:57.751
That's alright.

15:58.125 --> 15:59.876
You won't be here every day.

15:59.999 --> 16:01.250
I'll have to do it myself.

16:04.459 --> 16:05.500
Let me do it.

16:07.959 --> 16:09.459
Alright, then you
scoop this up.

16:09.999 --> 16:11.167
I'll make a coffee.

16:56.167 --> 16:57.959
Grandpa, do you feel cold?

16:59.292 --> 17:00.417
As usual.

17:01.999 --> 17:04.375
Saji uncle buys alcohol for
you, doesn't he?

17:06.876 --> 17:08.292
Right!

17:10.751 --> 17:18.125
Ask your father to bring some of his
home-brewed arrack.

17:18.167 --> 17:19.959
As if that's so necessary now!

17:20.876 --> 17:23.500
His Cholesterol and Uric acid
levels are high, already.

17:53.959 --> 17:55.792
I'm not allowed to drink
Coffee either.

17:56.999 --> 17:58.792
How can one live without
anything at all?

18:01.500 --> 18:03.375
After a certain age,

18:04.500 --> 18:06.999
This level of caution
is unnecessary.

18:08.751 --> 18:12.999
Without eating or drinking
to one's content,

18:14.834 --> 18:16.959
What is the use of
living a long life?

18:22.792 --> 18:25.042
Kurian brought a bottle for me.

18:25.999 --> 18:27.792
She has hidden it somewhere.

18:28.959 --> 18:30.292
Easter is around the corner,

18:30.834 --> 18:33.999
Drinking too much is not good
for your kidney or liver.

18:34.751 --> 18:36.918
Hospital bills will cost a lot.

18:38.417 --> 18:39.709
That's also true.

18:40.375 --> 18:41.834
I have become old.

18:43.292 --> 18:47.999
It is pointless to spend
money on me now.

18:49.375 --> 18:54.209
Those who love you would like to
see you around for a little longer.

18:57.459 --> 18:59.334
How innocent does he act with you!

18:59.751 --> 19:01.709
Sometimes he's entirely different.

19:02.209 --> 19:03.709
Gets too adamant.

19:05.083 --> 19:06.999
The eldest son has got
the same genes.

19:07.667 --> 19:09.542
As soon as I get out of sight,

19:09.626 --> 19:11.375
He starts yelling 'Rani...Rani'.

19:12.834 --> 19:14.375
Sometimes I feel bad for him.

19:14.792 --> 19:16.125
He's like a child.

19:17.334 --> 19:20.334
Who knows what we would
turn into as age hits us?

19:21.500 --> 19:24.417
Your mother-in-law used to
be even more intense.

19:24.876 --> 19:26.626
Jaya has told me about her.

19:27.250 --> 19:29.334
Luckily she died before I came.

19:30.834 --> 19:33.500
Look, I'm just blabbering away.

19:33.542 --> 19:34.500
I know.

19:35.999 --> 19:38.959
Papa doesn't bad mouth, at least!

19:40.250 --> 19:41.999
His face reflects what's
in his mind.

19:44.167 --> 19:45.792
Not really!

19:46.334 --> 19:49.042
He complained to me that you
don't let him drink.

19:50.292 --> 19:52.125
He asks me sometimes.

19:52.667 --> 19:54.542
I'm very strict with him
in this matter.

19:55.083 --> 19:56.250
Then he stops.

19:58.667 --> 19:59.999
See if this is crispy enough,

20:10.500 --> 20:12.626
Have you gone home recently?

20:13.959 --> 20:15.375
It's been two months.

20:19.292 --> 20:21.500
I'll ask Jaya or Celine.

20:21.542 --> 20:23.125
To stay here for a day or
two so that I can go.

20:24.125 --> 20:26.209
Mamma's legs are too weak.

20:27.459 --> 20:29.167
Now Aneeta is home too.

20:29.876 --> 20:31.959
She wants to do her
Masters at Bangalore.

20:31.999 --> 20:33.125
Mamma is stressed about it.

20:34.459 --> 20:35.834
I have an uncle,

20:36.709 --> 20:38.959
He's the one who
stresses mamma out.

20:39.918 --> 20:42.959
He says that the girls who go
to Bangalore turn into sluts.

20:43.709 --> 20:45.876
When a decision is
being made at home,

20:45.918 --> 20:47.834
Keep such idiots out of it.

20:47.876 --> 20:49.250
It is easier said than done.

20:49.959 --> 20:52.542
If Pappa was alive,
he would've let her study anywhere.

20:53.999 --> 20:55.667
She cries saying the same.

20:55.999 --> 20:57.334
We talked yesterday as well.

20:58.999 --> 21:01.292
Pappa used to give
her a special care!

21:02.792 --> 21:04.334
He hasn't beaten her even once.

21:10.999 --> 21:13.709
Bangalore is not such
a problematic place.

21:13.751 --> 21:15.792
That way, trouble can be
found anywhere.

21:17.542 --> 21:19.918
I know a few people in Bangalore.

21:19.959 --> 21:22.209
There was one Sister Maria
who did B.Ed with me.

21:22.667 --> 21:23.959
I shall ask her.

21:25.999 --> 21:27.542
If she's with Nuns,

21:28.083 --> 21:29.417
Mamma would also be relieved.

21:31.918 --> 21:32.959
It's okay.

21:33.500 --> 21:34.834
We can take care of this.

21:36.292 --> 21:39.334
Saji wouldn't proactively help
me with these things.

21:42.959 --> 21:45.417
Saji uncle is an introvert, right?

21:45.459 --> 21:46.459
Yeah,

21:46.500 --> 21:47.417
He must be!

21:50.042 --> 21:51.918
But, sometimes I feel bad for him.

22:26.209 --> 22:27.792
