After all, your daughter is back.

27:26.792 --> 27:28.209
It's not like the old days.

27:29.250 --> 27:30.999
Everybody make small mistakes.

27:38.876 --> 27:41.250
Let's be glad that she's still intact.

27:45.250 --> 27:48.500
Even if she is not,

27:49.125 --> 27:51.083
There's one Doctor
Selvarajan in Theni,

27:51.959 --> 27:53.709
He is the best to deal
with such matters.

27:54.834 --> 27:56.250
I know him personally.

28:02.167 --> 28:03.459
Tell me if you want to pay a visit.

