these days?

38:16.959 --> 38:18.417
Maybe it's his age.

38:19.500 --> 38:21.292
And it's not the old times anymore.

38:22.375 --> 38:25.959
All this TV and cinema are getting
into his head.

38:35.375 --> 38:37.542
His teacher had rung me.

38:38.167 --> 38:41.459
Apparently he said something vulgar
to a girl at school.

38:43.918 --> 38:45.042
That too,

38:45.125 --> 38:46.751
To a girl older to him!

38:49.834 --> 38:53.459
We often think that our children are
incapable of things like this.

38:54.083 --> 38:55.459
What did he say?

38:56.500 --> 38:57.626
He won't tell me.

38:59.125 --> 39:00.417
Probably he's afraid.

39:02.125 --> 39:04.042
The teacher said that it's really bad.

39:05.292 --> 39:07.042
They exaggerate these things.

39:09.334 --> 39:11.834
When you get time, talk to him.

39:12.042 --> 39:12.876
Sure.

39:12.918 --> 39:14.959
He'd open up to you.

39:15.292 --> 39:16.209
I'll do that.

39:35.626 --> 39:36.876
One more game?

40:03.626 --> 40:04.834
I've to go meet Tony.

40:05.417 --> 40:07.083
Why are you meeting him every day?

40:09.250 --> 40:10.626
When will brother Sony come?

40:10.792 --> 40:11.999
He will be late.

40:12.959 --> 40:13.918
Where did he go?

